<div id="learn-more">
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <h4 class="mt-4 mb-3 text-center pt-5">About Us</h4>

    <p class="text-center mt-4 mx-3">
    We started the Quick Favor Club on the premise of Adam Grant's "five-minute favor", popularized in his bestselling book <%= link_to "Give and Take", "https://www.adamgrant.net/give-and-take" %>.
    The idea behind these <i>quick</i> favors is simple: we can all find ways of adding high value to othersâ€™ lives at a low personal cost.
    </p>

    <p class="text-center">
    Our network is an <strong>invite-only community of do'ers that believe in helping others <i>conveniently</i> but <i>impactfully</i></strong>.
    This philosophy and behavior is contagious, and by paying it forward, the return on a favor fulfilled could be exponential.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-5 mb-4 text-center">Our Values</h4>

    <ul>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>We value reciprocity</strong>: Please aim to complete favors for others - our network is only as powerful as your willingness to help &#127867;</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>We value your time</strong>: All favors should be quick to fulfill (no more than 5 minutes!) & do-able from a computer or mobile device.</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>We value privacy</strong>: No contact information will be shared beyond your LinkedIn account (should you choose to provide it).</li>
      <li class="mb-2"><strong>We <i>don't</i> value spam and &#129324;</strong>: Favor requests submitted online will automatically go out via email to all members. Ideally, wait a day after receiving a new request to submit one of your own.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="center mt-5">
      <div class="d-flex">
        <p><strong>Want in?&nbsp; </strong></p> <%= link_to "Contact us", root_path(anchor: 'contact'), class: "font-weight-bold" %>&nbsp;&#128522;
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <h3 class="text-center my-4">Need some help?</h3>
    <% else %>
      <h3 class="text-center my-4">Let's Connect</h3>
    <% end %>

    <%= simple_form_for @inquiry do |f| %>
      <% if user_signed_in? == false %>
        <%= f.input :first_name, required: true %>
        <%= f.input :last_name, required: true %>
        <%= f.input :email, required: true %>
        <%= f.input :subject, collection: [ "Interested to join", "Interested to learn more", "Other" ] %>
        <%= f.input :message, :as => :text, :input_html => { 'rows' => 2 } %>
      <% else %>
        <%= f.input :subject, collection: [ "Requesting an introduction", "Problem with application", "General question", "Other" ] %>
        <%= f.input :message, hint: "If you'd like an introduction, please include the full name of the person you'd like to be introduced to and a quick statement of why", :as => :text, :input_html => { 'rows' => 4 }, required: true %>
      <% end %>

      <div class="center">
        <%= f.button :submit, 'Submit', class: "btn btn-primary btnHomeLight mt-4" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

</div>
